metadata.name: Monday Morning 1/1
metadata.description:
Culture of a lightning rod, appreciated on its own terms. Studious contemporary, with worn influences on thrifted sleeves. A shabby New York un-encumbrance of faux-opulence. Puff sleeve turndown collar high waist pleated neon skirt, two piece blazer set. Beaten silver choker necklace, crystal layered sequined clutch dosed in a deep shade of light steel blue. 

Synth Graph: a center front view, close up, 2020, photograph of a beautiful young 24 year old female model wearing knee high pink wedge boots, blue crystal purses, orange leather skirt, walking down manhattan in the late 1980s. Sampler: plms, steps: 75, scale: 11.
